OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a rather cloudy day.
OL,6,FSome patchy light rain at first,
OL,7,Fotherwise mainly dry with some
OL,8,Fbrightness coming through at times.
OL,9,FRather warm and humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy but dry evening
OL,12,Facross most parts. Cloud will thicken
OL,13,Fovernight with some rain spreading
OL,14,Finto Argyll by the morning.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Facross Argyll. Mainly dry with bright
OL,18,Fspells elsewhere and feeling warm..
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
