OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain across Argyll will clear
OL,7,Fduring Monday. Otherwise it will be
OL,8,Fdry with plenty of warm sunshine
OL,9,Fexpected.
